OL,3,CCouncil carers strike over
OL,4,C'outrageous' system where they had to
OL,5,C'work for free'
OL,7,FEssential care workers in Plymouth
OL,8,Fhave gone on strike due to
OL,9,F"disgraceful management practices" by
OL,10,Fthe city council, according to Unite
OL,11,Fthe Union.
OL,13,FIndependence at Home provides support
OL,14,Fand care across the city for
OL,15,Fvulnerable adults - including people
OL,16,Fwith mental health issues, substance
OL,17,Faddictions and terminal illnesses.
