OL,3,CCouncil carers strike over
OL,4,C'outrageous' system where they had to
OL,5,C'work for free'
OL,7,FThe care services were brought back
OL,8,Funder the control of Plymouth City
OL,9,FCouncil in 2019 and has operated a
OL,10,F"shortfall shift" system.
OL,12,FUnite says Independent at Home's
OL,13,Fmanagement were recording the time
OL,14,Fbetween home visits or appointments
OL,15,Fthat were cancelled at short notice as
OL,16,F"downtime".
