OL,3,CCouncil carers strike over
OL,4,C'outrageous' system where they had to
OL,5,C'work for free'
OL,7,FRachael said: "A little bit of
OL,8,Fcompensation and an apology would be
OL,9,Fnice. It's been removed now, yes, but
OL,10,Ffor five years we really, really were
OL,11,Fnot happy about it - it was so unfair."
OL,13,FRachael is one of nearly 50 care
OL,14,Fworkers striking from 25 November
OL,15,Fthrough to 1 December and again from
OL,16,F23 December to 29 December over the
OL,17,Fissue.
