OL,7,FMaggie Latcham has worked for
OL,8,FIndependence at Home. She said: "It's
OL,9,Fa shame it's had to come to this," she
OL,10,Fsaid. "We care about our customers, we
OL,11,Fcare about the service we provide - so
OL,12,Ffor it to come to this is really sad.
OL,14,F"But we have to make a stand."
OL,16,FPlymouth City Council has said it is
OL,17,F"working hard" to find a resolution
OL,18,Fand wants to "minimise the impact" of
OL,19,Fthe strike on people who are currently
OL,20,Faccessing the service.
