OL,3,CCouncil carers strike over
OL,4,C'outrageous' system where they had to
OL,5,C'work for free'
OL,7,FSharon Graham, the general secretary
OL,8,Ffor Unite, has said: "This is an
OL,9,Foutrageous way to treat vital staff
OL,10,Fwho do some of the most essential yet
OL,11,Fdifficult work imaginable ` caring for
OL,12,Fthe most vulnerable in our society.
OL,14,F"Plymouth City Council is treating
OL,15,Fthem appallingly by expecting them to
OL,16,Fwork for free to make up 'lost time'.
OL,17,FThis clearly isn't free time as care
OL,18,Fworkers remain on duty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
