OL,7,FA Plymouth City Council spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Due to a dispute over
OL,9,Fcontractual arrangements (which are no
OL,10,Flonger in place), we are aware that a
OL,11,Fnumber of staff members are likely to
OL,12,Ftake part in industrial action next
OL,13,Fweek.
OL,15,F"This affects our Independence at Home
OL,16,Fre-ablement service, which helps
OL,17,Fpeople who need extra support when
OL,18,Freturning home after a stay in
OL,19,Fhospital.
