OL,5,C'work for free'
OL,7,F"We are working hard to seek to
OL,8,Fresolve the dispute and minimise the
OL,9,Fimpact of the strike on people who are
OL,10,Fcurrently accessing the service.
OL,12,F"We are disappointed that it has
OL,13,Freached this stage given the dispute
OL,14,Fis linked to contractual arrangements
OL,15,Ffollowing staff consultation around
OL,16,Ffive years ago.
OL,18,F"We are in ongoing discussions with
OL,19,Fthe union to try to find a resolution
OL,20,Fas swiftly as possible."
