OL,7,FJoseph Murphy, the regional officer
OL,8,Ffor Unite, says the actions of
OL,9,FPlymouth City Council have been
OL,10,F"extremely disappointing" and there
OL,11,Fhas been a "failure to engage" with
OL,12,FUnite in recent months.
OL,14,FMr Murphy said: "Our members have an
OL,15,Funselfish instinct to care, and for
OL,16,Fthem to be put in the position where
OL,17,Fthey have to strike to be heard and
OL,18,Frespected is simply unacceptable.
